    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore levels</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049010/extras/103b798be17e6325142b9d43cd0f5efc.poster.avif?t=1741634773\" width=800 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049010/extras/103b798be17e6325142b9d43cd0f5efc.webm?t=1741634773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049010/extras/103b798be17e6325142b9d43cd0f5efc.mp4?t=1741634773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In each randomly generated level, you must reach the exit. But beware of monsters, traps and curses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the end of the fifth level, a boss fight awaits you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build item combos !</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049010/extras/24b71f9e5033d4a4facf73b558e7c7d4.poster.avif?t=1741634773\" width=424 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049010/extras/24b71f9e5033d4a4facf73b558e7c7d4.webm?t=1741634773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049010/extras/24b71f9e5033d4a4facf73b558e7c7d4.mp4?t=1741634773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 80 items to unlock. Find as much item as you can during a run, with treasure rooms, shop and casinos and build devastating combos !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Select Curses</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049010/extras/7b753d53fe0229fbf60223efd58c384d.poster.avif?t=1741634773\" width=520 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049010/extras/7b753d53fe0229fbf60223efd58c384d.webm?t=1741634773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049010/extras/7b753d53fe0229fbf60223efd58c384d.mp4?t=1741634773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress further into the dungeon. Every level finished you must select a curse that will be applied for all next levels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each curse affect the experience in a level in a meaningful way, like adding toxic puddles everywhere, mines in the walls,<br>spawning bombs on enemie's death, and much more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Will you be able to reach the bottom of the Dungeon ?</p>",
